				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As often as BRD/WHM is used, there are flaws to it. Mind makes the HP flow with healing, and even if you're a Taru Bard, your Mind is only decent. And since WHM would be a sub, its MP drops somewhat dramatically. I use BRD/RDM, and I was once in a Party with a leader who thought I could heal everyone. That didn't work. Having WHM as sub won't make things a lot better either. Unless you feel safer having a little extra cure, the generic Party would want a full WHM to do the healing.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
