				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">It is correct to say that a BRD/WHM or BRD/RDM would have insufficient MP to be the main healer in the PT.  However, there is no other worthwhile sub that a BRD can have in an exp PT.   A BRD who has the ability to throw some emergency cures or one who can fill in for the resting main healer for a little bit is a worthwhile asset.  
<br />

<br />
MND is not all its cracked up to be either.  If your healing skill is capped or near-capped, you need about 10 MND to increase your curing power by 1.  If you have low MND, you can easily circumvent this problem by making sure to raise your healing magic skill.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
			</tr>
